      <h1 class="h2">What affects Tidal Variation?</h1>
      <The>Have you ever wondered how much the height of high tide itself might vary? How about the difference between high tide and low tide in metres? The height of high tide and the difference between high tide and low tide, known as the tidal range, can vary significantly depending on several factors. Let's explore these factors and their influence on tidal variations... </p>
      <br>
